column5: I'll be on Jumping Caribou lake next week... but here's a start for you...  http://www.vacationcottagerentals.com/

EH! Try lake Tomiko.. I recommend Moose Point Cottages.. nice sandy beach. room for kids to run affordable rates. good Walleye and Pike fishin' plenty of bass on lakes Tomiko and Chebogomog H/K or try Camp Horizon in Feild On, good rates sandy beach ,walleye pike ,bass ,muskie. confectionnary, pontoon rental private cottages. H/K. it's on lake Muskasong.  Good Luck!
